{
  "stem": "2758.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And my father worked at the same-- in the same kind of factory that he worked before.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I was in enrolled in a German school in Holland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] My father thought it would-- I didn't know the language, so it would be easier for me to go and learn the curriculum and learn Dutch at the same time.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It was a very nice school, very good school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I was tested, and I was-- skipped a class.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I had a wonderful teacher.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And one day, they got a visitor from Germany, a SS man-- SR man-- with the brown uniforms and the red arm band.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And we had to-- the school had to perform-- it was an assembly.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "He researched what was being taught there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And we went up on the roof to a theater in the school, and we had-- each class had to perform for him.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "One girl played the piano.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Some other's danced.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "There was a choir, some readings.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And my teacher decided that I should recite a very famous poem.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Well, I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I went onto the stage and recited this poem and-- very fiery.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And the SS man-- after I finished, everybody was applauding.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And he came down to the stage, and he shook my hand.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And I very nicely curtsied.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And then he turned to the audience and he said, now here you can see what a pure Aryan child can do.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then he turned to me and he asked me for my name, and I told him my name is Regina Rosenzweig.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he got furious.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He didn't say anything, but he got wet in the face.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my teacher was very reprimanded.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So isn't it ironic?",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
